title: #92Noon! Live From The Combine 2020
description: The FAN's Paul Allen, Producer Eric Nordquist, Paul Charchian and Ben Leber are live from the 2020 NFL Combine in Indiana! It's Speculation Central in this mug, featuring interviews with ESPN's Adam Schefter and Vikings GM, Rick Spielman.
